answers.body_markdown:
There is no issue with you code, But you haven&#39;t asked for External storage read permission.

Add following permission in your `AndroidManifest.xml` file

    &lt;manifest ...&gt;
        &lt;uses-permission android:name=&quot;android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE&quot; /&gt;
        ....
    &lt;/manifest&gt;

And ask for this permission at run time like shown in [Request App Permissions](https://developer.android.com/training/permissions/requesting).

